581
00:32:55,380 --> 00:32:57,500
life or if this were to come in my life.

582
00:32:57,500 --> 00:32:59,620
And I just, it would just destroy me.

583
00:32:59,620 --> 00:33:06,300
And the problem with that kind of thinking is that God's grace is sufficient in the moment.

584
00:33:06,300 --> 00:33:13,180
Not in advance, not in the hypothetical, when in the moment you find that God's grace

585
00:33:13,180 --> 00:33:16,820
