740
00:42:28,340 --> 00:42:30,500
Father, if there's some that are dealing with pride

741
00:42:30,500 --> 00:42:33,860
at whatever measure, whatever level it might be,

742
00:42:33,860 --> 00:42:37,340
would you help us this morning to humble ourselves?

743
00:42:37,340 --> 00:42:40,660
Would you help us to be clothed in humility?

744
00:42:41,700 --> 00:42:44,820
As we think about the example of our Lord and Savior

745
00:42:44,820 --> 00:42:47,020
who humbled himself

746
00:42:47,980 --> 00:42:50,140
and became obedient unto death,

747
00:42:50,140 --> 00:42:51,820
even the death of the cross,

748
00:42:53,580 --> 00:42:56,100
Lord, you are God.

749
00:42:56,100 --> 00:42:58,100
You left the throne of heaven,

750
00:42:58,100 --> 00:43:02,700
the glory to come to this sin-cursed world to die for us,

751
00:43:03,740 --> 00:43:05,700
to rise.

752
00:43:05,700 --> 00:43:07,780
Leave us an example

753
00:43:08,700 --> 00:43:12,220
and help us to be clothed in humility.

754
00:43:12,220 --> 00:43:14,060
Would you work in these moments of invitation

755
00:43:14,060 --> 00:43:15,720
as only you can?

756
00:43:15,720 --> 00:43:16,740
We'll give you the honor and glory

757
00:43:16,740 --> 00:43:17,860
for every decision that's made.

758
00:43:17,860 --> 00:43:19,660
For it's in Christ's name we pray.

759
00:43:19,660 --> 00:43:20,540
Would you stand with me?

760
00:43:20,540 --> 00:43:22,500
Heads are bowed, eyes are closed.

761
00:43:22,940 --> 00:43:25,100
Kimberly's gonna play quietly on the piano.

762
00:43:25,100 --> 00:43:26,580
If you're not sure of heaven,

763
00:43:26,580 --> 00:43:28,300
if you're a man, we have a brother Mark,

764
00:43:28,300 --> 00:43:29,380
he'll take a Bible and show you

765
00:43:29,380 --> 00:43:30,780
you can know for sure that heaven's your home.

766
00:43:30,780 --> 00:43:31,980
Holly's here.

767
00:43:31,980 --> 00:43:34,020
If you're a lady, don't know that heaven is your home,

768
00:43:34,020 --> 00:43:35,980
we'd love to take a Bible and show you how to know.

